<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd">
<HTML>
	<HEAD>
		<META HTTP-EQUIV="Content-Type" CONTENT="text/html; charset=utf-8">
		<META NAME="resource-type" CONTENT="document">
		<LINK REL="stylesheet" HREF="index.css" TYPE="text/css" MEDIA="all">
		<TITLE>Writing UNIX Manual Pages</TITLE>
	</HEAD>
	<BODY>
		<DIV>
			% cat manpages.7
			<BR>
			.Dd $Mdocdate$
			<BR>
			.Dt MANUALS 7
			<BR>
			.Os
			<BR>
			.Sh NAME
			<BR>
			.Nm <SPAN CLASS="vis">UNIX Manual Pages</SPAN>
			<BR>
			.Nd <SPAN CLASS="vis">structure, style, and composition</SPAN>
			<BR>
			.\"
			<BR>
			.\"
			<BR>
			.Sh <SPAN CLASS="h1">DESCRIPTION</SPAN>
			<BR>
			.\"
			<BR>
			.Em <SPAN CLASS="vis em">A utility without good documentation is of no utility at all.</SPAN>
			<BR>
			.Pp
			<DIV CLASS="vis">
			So you've written a utility, library, or driver (or started writing one), and you want to document your work.
			<BR>
			How do you get from code to
			</DIV>
			.Xr <A
			HREF="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=man&amp;apropos=0&amp;sektion=0&amp;manpath=OpenBSD+Current&amp;arch=i386&amp;format=html">man</A> 1
			<DIV CLASS="vis">
			output?
			</DIV>
			.Pp
			<DIV CLASS="vis">
			This site is a resource for composing well-formed and maintainable UNIX manuals in
			</DIV>
			.Xr <A
			HREF="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=mdoc&amp;apropos=0&amp;sektion=0&amp;manpath=OpenBSD+Current&amp;arch=i386&amp;format=html">mdoc</A> 7 
			<SPAN CLASS="vvis">,</SPAN>
			<DIV CLASS="vis">
			a language designed specifically for UNIX manuals.
			</DIV>
			.Pp
			<DIV CLASS="vis">
			For the time being, this site contains only links to existing resources and a mailing list for specific questions.
			<BR>
			Eventually we will post FAQ's and tutorials.
			</DIV>
			.\"
			<BR>
			.Sh <SPAN CLASS="h1">SEE ALSO</SPAN>
			<BR>
			.\"
			<DIV CLASS="vis">
			Our reference platform for UNIX manual formatting:
			</DIV>
			.Pp
			<BR>
			.Lk <A HREF="http://mdocml.bsd.lv/">http://mdocml.bsd.lv/</A>
			<BR>
			.Pp
			<DIV CLASS="vis">
			This page as a manual:
			</DIV>
			.Pp
			<BR>
			.Lk <A HREF="index.7">index.7</A>
			<BR>
			.Lk <A HREF="index.7.html">index.7.html</A>
			<BR>
			.Lk <A HREF="index.7.txt">index.7.txt</A>
			<BR>
		</DIV>
	</BODY>
</HTML>
